item.description:

Video featured by http://skandalim.ru suggests lost control of his vehicle, and slammed into stock shelves holding thousands of bottles of Cognac and vodka. The chain reaction soon left him very much under the influence of drink. The accident will leave the alcohol retailer with a nasty financial hangover. It's estimated over 150 thousands dollars worth of stock was downed.

item.title: Kate, Her Story - Natalie Morales Interview 1 of 5
item.description:
Kate, Her Story - Natalie Morales Interview 1 of 5
As the episodes of Jon and Kate Plus 8 dwindle, this week we get to see a full on hour interview with just Kate - it's not counted as an actual episode. Most people are ready to gouge out their eyes and avoid listening to Kate give her BS PR answers to the same questions again... but this one's different. She actually does get some interesting new topics, and seems more genuine. I'm particularly interested in the questions about her childhood and relationship with her family. I don't know much of what went on... anyone know why the grandparents are out of the picture? I would imagine they would have had to have done something pretty awful to be excluded from the gosselin childrens' lives. Those grandparent hugs sure meant a lot to me growing up, I would hope there's a really really good reason to keep those hugs from those kids. Parts 2 through 5 are up

item.title: Agressão: Barraco de Claudia Leitte e Alex Lopes! TV Aratu - SBT!
item.description:
Agressão: Barraco de Claudia Leitte e Alex Lopes! TV Aratu - SBT!
A cantora convidou o repórter e sua equipe para entrarem na coletiva de imprensa que estava tendo no local. Claudia já conhecia ele por ler possíveis notícias maliciosas sobre ela no site do jornalista. No meio da coletiva Claudia perguntou o que o mesmo tinha contra ela, foi daí que começou a confusão, quando o jornalista do SBT disse que ela não era obrigada a ler o site e que de que a carioca deveria respeitar o seu trabalho, mesmo que fosse com críticas. O jornalista afirma ter sido agredido e ameaçado por seguranças e pelo marido da cantora, logo após ser "convidado" a entrar na sala que aparece no fim do vídeo. Saiba como tudo começou aqui: http://ego.globo.com/Gente/Noticias/0,,MUL1363318-9798,00-CLAUDIA+LEITTE+DA+LICAO+DE+MORAL+EM+JORNALISTA.html
